title: Bronze forever adc looking for a sup duo.
body:
Would like to duo with a sup who is a passionate sup. I loved playing  sup my self but have goten sick of it. To much to docus on the mind for me. I just wanna farm then kill then take objectives and have a sup telling me where to go next... 
Im more of a follower then a alpha dog in this game. So someone with better experience then me would be a bonus. (Not someone who is too good....) Because I wont keep up. My ambition in non real life is to make silver before I retire after playing this game for 10 years (NEXT YEAR IS MY TENTH YEAR OF THIS). Im not kidding.

replies.body: Maybe ill get there on my own, you never know..
aha, add me ill take you to silver - Taknan jr
